data.description: Move-in ready with quick access to I-49 and all of what NWA has to offer! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has a spacious interior split floor plan with an open concept living and kitchen area.  The master suite has tray ceilings, a large walk-in closet, and a master bath with a walk in shower and separate jetted whirlpool tub. You will find the laundry room is also surprisingly large.  Stepping onto the back deck you will enjoy the large fenced backyard overlooking fields with no back neighbors. Schedule your appointment today to see for yourself before it is gone!
